enhanced_by.reason: The readContent method is invoked within fromContents to parse the provided content strings into OpenAPI specifications, which are then used for comparison.
fromContents relies on fromSpecifications to perform the actual comparison of the parsed OpenAPI specifications.
Both fromContents and fromSpecifications return a ChangedOpenApi object, indicating that the assertions for fromContents can be informed by the assertions used for fromSpecifications.
Both methods handle null OpenAPI specifications and throw exceptions if null values are encountered, suggesting similar exception handling in test cases.
